sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Admin as ChuToChuc_Admin
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgSvc as OrganizationService
participant DeptDb as Mongo_Department
participant ChannelDb as Mongo_Channel

Note over Admin,ChannelDb: Chặng 1 - Quản trị cấu trúc phòng ban và kênh
Admin->>Client: Tạo phòng ban
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/departments
Gateway->>OrgSvc: protect + authorize
OrgSvc->>DeptDb: Insert department
OrgSvc-->>Client: 201

Admin->>Client: Tạo kênh trong phòng ban
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/.../channels
Gateway->>OrgSvc: protect + authorize
OrgSvc->>ChannelDb: Insert channel
OrgSvc-->>Client: 201
